---
title: Double Golden Fish & Chargrilled Capsicum Mayo with Roast Veggie Coin Toss
description: Fish is one of those dinner time dishes that demands attention. This one is golden, drizzled in a chargrillled capsicum mayo, and served atop a bed of roasted veggies. Every bite is a delightful surprise!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65ded1ef5a1abdbdbb7a34e5-1cef198c.jpeg
